@startuml
[*] --> DisplayJourneyDetails
DisplayJourneyDetails --> ActivateDrivingModeOrOtherOptions : activate driving mode or other options
ActivateDrivingModeOrOtherOptions --> SelectPlaceToEat : select place to eat
SelectPlaceToEat --> ViewMenuAndPlaceOrder : view menu and place order if hungry
ViewMenuAndPlaceOrder --> InformRelevantAuthoritiesInCaseOfAccident : inform authorities in case of accident
InformRelevantAuthoritiesInCaseOfAccident --> SendNotificationsDuringDrivingOrInCaseOfAccident : send notifications during driving or in case of accident
SendNotificationsDuringDrivingOrInCaseOfAccident --> ProvideFeedbackUponCompletionOfJourney : provide feedback upon completion of journey
ProvideFeedbackUponCompletionOfJourney --> [*] : logout
@enduml
